author: yahoo
title: First Data rises 2.6 pct in debut, valued at $14.4 bln - Yahoo Finance
text:
Oct 15 (Reuters) - Shares in First Data Corp rose 2.6 percent in their debut on Thursday, valuing the payment processor at $14.42 billion in the largest initial public offering this year.
The company raised $2.56 billion by selling 160 million shares at $16 each, below the indicated range of $18 to $20.
(Reporting by Rachel Chitra and Richa Naidu in Bengaluru; Editing by Ted Kerr)
Currency First Data Corp
